Saya datang untuk ambil ubat preskripsi.

422
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:42,311
Preskripsi?

423
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:44,260
Maaf. Kami sudah tutup hari ini.

424
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:46,340
Saya dengar ada tabib wanita ajaib di sini.

425
00:20:46,990 --> 00:20:47,630
Saya dah cakap.

426
00:20:47,670 --> 00:20:48,990
Kami sudah tutup hari ini.

427
00:20:49,740 --> 00:20:50,500
Sabar dulu!

428
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:52,340
Sila tunggu di luar.

429
00:20:53,820 --> 00:20:55,630
Awak masuk tanpa kebenaran.

430
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:57,020
Itu menceroboh.

431
