472
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:48,753
Putera Yunnuo, tolong berhenti.

473
00:22:48,870 --> 00:22:50,044
Biar saya ambil daun teratai.

474
00:22:50,446 --> 00:22:52,689
♪Aku akan mengikutimu ke mana saja♪

475
00:22:53,043 --> 00:22:56,901
